snippet.title: Stephen Wonderboy Thompson
snippet.description:
Official Channel of UFC Welterweight Stephen "Wonderboy" Thompson.

I began training in the art of Kempo Karate at age 3 and began competing in kickboxing at the age of 15.  I amassed an undefeated kickboxing record of 57 wins and 0 losses.
After training with fighters such as George "Rush" St Pierre and Suga Rashad Evans, I made the transition to MMA.  I have a current record of 15-4-1 with notable wins over Johny Hendricks, Jake Ellenberger, Robert Whittaker, Jorge Masvidal, and Rory Macdonald.

Thank you all for tuning in and I hope you enjoy!

Upload Schedule:
